32
00:01:07,320 --> 00:01:09,810
So just like dating,
you need to figure out

33
00:01:09,810 --> 00:01:12,090
how you're gonna approach the stock market

34
00:01:12,090 --> 00:01:14,130
so that you get the results you want.

35
00:01:14,130 --> 00:01:16,620
There are two strategies
you can choose from:

36
00:01:16,620 --> 00:01:19,800
the technical or the fundamental approach.

37
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:21,690
Both of these options are very different,

38
00:01:21,690 --> 00:01:23,880
so let's quickly go
over what they involve.

39
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:27,360
Technical analysis is mainly
for short-term day traders.

40
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:30,480
They use charts and price
action to identify patterns

41
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:32,700
that supposedly help them predict

42
00:01:32,700 --> 00:01:35,790
if a stock is gonna go up
or down in the short-term.

43
00:01:35,790 --> 00:01:38,880
I use the word supposedly
because in my opinion

44
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:40,980
most of the people using this strategy

45
00:01:40,980 --> 00:01:42,360
are glorified gamblers.

46
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:44,940
Is it possible that
they trade successfully?

47
00:01:44,940 --> 00:01:48,960
Yes, but more than 95%,
a day traders lose money

48
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,010
rather than making it,

49
00:01:50,010 --> 00:01:51,480
according to The Motley Fool.

50
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:54,480
Fundamental analysis is
like being a detective

51
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,650
for a company.

52
00:01:55,650 --> 00:01:57,030
You look at everything,

53
00:01:57,030 --> 00:02:00,570
from their financial reports
to how well-known the brand is

54
00:02:00,570 --> 00:02:02,100
and who's running the show.

55
00:02:02,100 --> 00:02:04,740
All these pieces of
information help you understand

56
00:02:04,740 --> 00:02:07,020
how the company is doing now

57
00:02:07,020 --> 00:02:09,600
and how it might perform in the future.

58
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:12,180
This approach can help
you pick a range of stocks

59
00:02:12,180 --> 00:02:14,040
that can make you a nice amount of money

60
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:16,050
over a three to 10 year period.

61
