112
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,600
So to find the balance sheet,

113
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:09,090
just head to the stock
you're interested in.

114
00:04:09,090 --> 00:04:13,683
For this example, I'm
gonna pick Coca-Cola.

115
00:04:14,820 --> 00:04:17,970
Scroll down the page,
click on the Financials,

116
00:04:17,970 --> 00:04:22,530
